# Vendored upstream Randovania repos — not redistributed.
# We use them as reference clones during dev. End users get the same code
# via `pip install open-dread-rando open-dread-rando-exlaunch`. The starter
# patcher template we actually need at runtime is bundled inside the
# apworld at apworld/dread_archipelago/data/starter_preset_patcher.json.
# vendor/CHANGES.md (tracked) documents how to clone these locally.
